title: [Valdorn's Weaponry]
[Valdorn's Magic Shoppe]
[Valdorn's General Store]
description: A peacock feather fan hangs on one of the blue watered silk walls, and a mistwood beam ceiling rises overhead.  A brass flowerpot sits in one corner of a polished oak floor.  There is a series of low oak shelves on one side of the shop and a gilded maple table on the other.
